      "rationale": "Formal input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2. A one-at-a-time sensitivity analysis was performed voluntarily and confirmed that the RH prediction is most sensitive to inlet flow rate (±3.2% RH per ±5% flow rate variation), within acceptable bounds."
